function CreateAccount(){

    forceReturn = false;
    $(".na_pw_div_search_message").text("");
    $(".na_pw_div_error_message").text("");
    if($("#pw_comm_SearchAccounts_cmatAccountName").val() == "") {

         $(".na_pw_div_error_message").text("Please enter the Account Name"); 
    }
    else if($("#pw_comm_SearchAccounts_Line1").val() == "") {
        forceReturn = true;
         $(".na_pw_div_error_message").text("Please enter Address"); 
    }
    else if($("#pw_comm_SearchAccounts_City").val() == "") {
        forceReturn = true;
         $(".na_pw_div_error_message").text("Please enter name of the City"); 
    }
    else if($("#pw_comm_SearchAccounts_country").val() == "") {
        forceReturn = true;
         $(".na_pw_div_error_message").text("Please enter name of the Country"); 
    }
    else if($("#pw_comm_SearchAccounts_PostalCode").val() == "") {
        forceReturn = true;
         $(".na_pw_div_error_message").text("Please enter Postal Code"); 
    }

    if(forceReturn) {
        return;
    }

    var payLoad = {
        "cacheInstanceId" : "-1",
        "fromPunchin" : false,
        "headlessMode" : true,
        "configData" : {
            "actionType" : "CREATE",
            "quoteNumber": PW_NA_QUOTE_NUMBER,
            "transactionId" : PW_NA_QUOTE_ID,
            "companyName" : $("#pw_comm_SearchAccounts_cmatAccountName").val(),

            "userType" : PW_NA_USER_TYPE,
            "userName" : PW_NA_USER_NAME
        },
        "criteria": {
            "fields": [
              "addressResponse"
            ]
        }
    }
    console.log(endPointURL);
    console.log(payLoad.configData);
    $(".na_pw_div_search_message").text("Add New Account : Sending account data to CMAT ..."); 
    customConfigure(endPointURL, payLoad).then((data) => {
        obj = JSON.parse(data.configData.addressResponse);

             $(".na_pw_div_search_message").text("Add New Account : Successfull response from CMAT ...");

        }
        
    }).catch((error) => {$(".na_pw_div_error_message").text(error)});
}

function customConfigure(configUrl, payLoad) {
        $("#loading-overlay-pw-comm").show();
        return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {
     $.ajax({
                 url: configUrl,
                 headers: {
                      "X-Cpq-Csrf-Token": PW_BM_CSRF_TOKEN,
                      "Accept": "application/json",
                      "Content-Type": "application/json" 
                  },
                 type: 'POST',
                 data: JSON.stringify(payLoad),
                 dataType : 'json',
                 async: true
              }).done(function(data) {
                   $("#loading-overlay-pw-comm").hide();
                   resolve(data);
              }).fail(function(error) {
                   $("#loading-overlay-pw-comm").hide();
                   reject(error);
              }); 
    }); 
}

function getTableData(tableData) {
    var table_data = [];
    var filler = "";
    if(PW_NA_SEARCH_TYPE == "ACCOUNTS") {
        filler = "account";
    }
    else {
        filler = "contact";
    }
    if(tableData !== null && tableData.length > 0) {
        var codataScrub = tableData.replace(/(?:\r\n|\r|\n)/g, '');
        var rawData = JSON.parse(codataScrub);   
        for(i=0; i<rawData.length;i++){
            obj = rawData[i];
            var objData;
            var objDataContact;
            var objDataContactEdit;
            var selectButton
            if(PW_NA_SEARCH_TYPE == "ACCOUNTS") {
              objData = "data-accountCMATID='" + obj.cmatId + "' data-siteCMATID='" + obj.cmatSiteId + "' data-name='" + obj.companyName.replace(/'/g, '')
 + "'  data-street='" + obj.address1 + "'" + "' data-address2='" + obj.address2 + "'" + "' data-address3='" + obj.address3 + "'" + "' data-city='" + obj.city + "'" + "' data-state='" + obj.state + "'" + "' data-zipCode='" + obj.postalCode + "'" + "' data-country='" + obj.country + "'" + "' data-restrictedPartylist='" + obj.rplFLag + "'";
              selectButton = "<button class='pw_select_account_search_btn' " + objData + ">Select</button>";
            }
            else {

              objDataContact = "data-action=SET" + " data-siteCMATID='" + obj.cmatSiteId + "' data-fullName='" + obj.fullName + "' data-firstName='" + obj.firstName + "' data-lastName='" + obj.lastName + "'  data-phone='" + obj.mainNumber + "'" + "' data-email='" + obj.emailId + "'" + "' data-contactId='" + obj._id + "'" + "' data-accountName='" + obj.accountName + "'";

              objDataContactEdit = "data-action=EDIT" + " data-siteCMATID='" + obj.cmatSiteId + "' data-fullName='" + obj.fullName + "' data-firstName='" + obj.firstName + "' data-lastName='" + obj.lastName + "'  data-phone='" + obj.mainNumber + "'" + "' data-email='" + obj.emailId + "'" + "' data-contactId='" + obj._id + "'" + "' data-accountName='" + obj.accountName + "'";
              selectButton = "<button class='pw_select_account_search_btn' " + objDataContact + ">Select</button>";
              selectButton += "  <button class='pw_select_account_search_btn' " + objDataContactEdit + ">Edit</button>";
            }

           
            row_data = [];
            row_data.push(selectButton);
            if(PW_NA_SEARCH_TYPE == "ACCOUNTS") {
                  row_data.push(obj.companyName);
                  row_data.push(obj.cmatId + "/" + obj.cmatSiteId);
                  row_data.push(obj.address1);
                  row_data.push(obj.city);
                  row_data.push(obj.state);
                  row_data.push(obj.postalCode);
                  row_data.push(obj.country);
            }
            else {
                  row_data.push(obj.emailId);
                  row_data.push(obj.firstName);
                  row_data.push(obj.lastName);
                  row_data.push(obj.fullName);
                  row_data.push(obj.mainNumber);
                  row_data.push(obj.cmatCompanyId);
                  row_data.push(obj.accountName);

            }
            table_data.push(row_data);
        }

        if(rawData.length == 0) {
                 if(PW_NA_LAUNCH == false) {
                         
                         if(PW_NA_SEARCH_TYPE == "ACCOUNTS") {
                            if(PW_NA_ACCOUNT_TYPE != "Sold To" && PW_NA_ACCOUNT_TYPE != "End Customer") {
                                 $('#pw_comm_CreateAccount_button').show();
                                 $(".na_pw_div_search_message").text("No matches found. Use a different search filter or create a new " + filler); 
                             }
                             else {
                                 $('#pw_comm_CreateAccount_button').hide();
                                 $(".na_pw_div_search_message").text("No matches found. Use a different search filter "); 
                             }

                         }
                         if(PW_NA_SEARCH_TYPE == "CONTACTS") {
                             $('#pw_comm_CreateContact_button').show();
                             $(".na_pw_div_search_message").text("No matches found. Use a different search filter or create a new " + filler); 
                         }
                }

        }
        else {
            if(PW_NA_LAUNCH == false) {
                $(".na_pw_div_search_message").text("Click the Select button to add the " + filler + " for " + PW_NA_ACCOUNT_TYPE + "."); 
                $('#pw_comm_CreateContact_button').hide();
            }
        }
        if(PW_NA_SEARCH_TYPE == "ACCOUNTS") {
                if(PW_NA_ACCOUNT_TYPE != "Sold To" && PW_NA_ACCOUNT_TYPE != "End Customer") {
                     $('#pw_comm_CreateAccount_button').show();
                 }
                 else {
                     $('#pw_comm_CreateAccount_button').hide();
                 }

        }
    }
    else {
         if(PW_NA_LAUNCH == false) {
            $(".na_pw_div_search_message").text("No matches found. Change the search filter or create a new " + filler); 
            if(PW_NA_SEARCH_TYPE == "ACCOUNTS") {

                 $('#pw_comm_CreateContact_button').show();

             }
         }
    }

    return table_data;

function performUpdateAction(updatedAccountString){
    $(".na_pw_div_error_message").text("");
    endPointURL = "https://netappinctest3.bigmachines.com/rest/v16/commerceDocumentsUcpqStandardCommerceProcessTransaction/481931730/actions/update_t_c";
    var payLoad = {
        "documents": {
            "accountsEditJson_t_c" : updatedAccountString
        },
        "criteria": {
            "state" : false,
            "fields" : [
                    "accountsJsonArray_t_c"
                ]
        },
        "cacheInstanceId": PW_NA_CHACHE_INSTANCE
    }

    customConfigure(endPointURL, payLoad).then((data) => {
        CXCPQUtil.setQuoteRevisionId(data.revisionId);
        if(PW_NA_SEARCH_TYPE == "ACCOUNTS") {
            var showContact = false;
            accObj = JSON.parse(updatedAccountString);
            actionType = accObj.actionType;
            if(actionType == "COPY_ACCOUNT") {
                accType = accObj.COPY_FROM;
                setCopiedAccountIds(data.documents.accountsJsonArray_t_c,accType);
                showContact = true;
            }
            else if(actionType == "CREATE_ACCOUNT") {
                showContact = false;
            }
            else {
                showContact = true;
                PW_NA_ACCOUNT_CMATID = accObj.accountCMATID;
                PW_NA_SITE_CMATID = accObj.siteCMATID;
            }
            if(showContact) {
                var optContact = $('#pw_comm_searchType option:contains("Contact")');
                optContact.prop('disabled', false);
                $(".na_pw_div_search_message").text(PW_NA_ACCOUNT_TYPE + " Account Updated. To add Contact, please select Contact from the Search Type. Please close the window when done.");
            }
            else {
                 $(".na_pw_div_search_message").text(PW_NA_ACCOUNT_TYPE + " Account Updated. Please close the window");
            }
        }
        else {
            $(".na_pw_div_search_message").text(PW_NA_ACCOUNT_TYPE  + " Contact Updated, please close the window."); 
        }
    }).catch((error) => {
        errStr = error.responseJSON.title;
        if (errStr.indexOf("Price List") >= 0) {
            errStr = errStr + " ; Country cannot be updated as it will impact current pricelist of the quote";
        }
        else if (errStr.indexOf("Inco Term") >= 0){
            errStr = errStr + " ; Country cannot be updated as it will impact current incoterm of the quote";
        }
        $(".na_pw_div_search_message").text("");
        $(".na_pw_div_error_message").text(errStr);
    });

}
